{
  "manifest": {
    "author": "Lattice",
    "description": "Exercises every feature of the spec in one document under the E3-S2 grammar: nested grids with subgrids and explicit placement (E2-S1); static, runtime, and computed variables (E3-S1/S2/S3); $var typed binding and ${} string templating (E3-S2); a select runtime input held in a variable-box and bound to an enum variable (E1-S3); both connection types — a static inline source and an http (query) connection (E4-S1/S2); a $secret reference that is redacted from the resolved tree (E4-S2); and a result-shape expectedResult contract on a bound table (E4-S3). The two tables are each wrapped in a block. Resolve with METRICS_API_TOKEN set: METRICS_API_TOKEN=xyz lattice resolve examples/kitchen-sink-dashboard.json — the token value never appears in the output. Conforms to https://lattice.dev/schemas/dashboard/1.0.0.",
